// Note that this test file doesn't contain tests for `maintainContext`. That will be handled in `Office_delegationCall`
// test file.
DelegationContext
└── When caller is authorized
    └── When ongoing delegation call
        ├── It should set the context correctly.
        ├── It should return `true` when `isOngoingDelegationCall` is called.
        ├── It should return `true` when `isOngoingDelegationCallForAccount` is called with the correct account.
        └── It should return `false` when `isOngoingDelegationCallForAccount` is called with an incorrect account.
